Figure 1 shows the rolling status of visits to enrollees. If the planned visit has been completed, the actual visit date is marked with a filled circle. If the visit is late being completed, the planned date is marked with a triangle. If the planned visit is pending, i.e., it is a future date, the planned date is marked with an open circle. The grey vertical line on the plot is centered at todays date.
